snippet.title: Bladestorm: The Hundred Years' War Intro Cinematic
snippet.description:
The intro cinematic to this under-apreciated 2007 gem. Sure it had bad voice acting and a raft of other problems but it was fun. 
Unfortunately it has little to no presence on Youtube, it deserves some love.
